                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Enfant, tu t'asseyais près de lui sur la mousse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Et tu lisais alors d'une voix calme et douce.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "D'un sage et vieux druide, ainsi, dans la forêt,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Disciple, je suivis l'enseignement secret.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "J'ai redit vos discours aux esprits des bruyères ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et ceux des bois taillis, des étangs, des rivières,",
