                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Entendais-tu sortir des plaintes étouffées ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Ces plaintes, cher enfant, étaient celles des fées :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "C'étaient leurs cris d'amour, leurs chants grêles, leurs vœux",
